I"é<h1 id="training">Training</h1>

<h2 id="create">Create</h2>

<p><strong>STEP-1</strong>: Click on <strong>New</strong> option and select <strong>Training</strong>. <strong>Training</strong> window will appear.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_201.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-2</strong>: Fill the details.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_202.png" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-3</strong>: Click on <strong>Add</strong> button to add employees who will attend training.  List of employees will appear. Select the employee and click on OK.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_203.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p><strong>STEP-4</strong>: Row will add in Applicability area. Fill effectiveness and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_204.png" alt="" /></p>

<h2 id="list">List</h2>

<p>Click on <strong>Employee</strong> menu and select <strong>Trainings</strong>. Trainings list will appear.</p>

<h2 id="edit">Edit</h2>

<p>Select the training from training list and right click on it. Select <strong>Edit Training</strong> option. Training form will appear. Edit the details and click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_205.jpg" alt="" /></p>

<p>In Edit mode, you can also upload training content in pdf format.</p>

<p>For this, click on <strong>Browse</strong> button and select training content. Click on <strong>Upload</strong> button. Click on <strong>Save</strong>.</p>

<p><img src="http://docs.risersoft.com/hrmnirvana/ImagesExt/image8_206.png" alt="" /></p>

<p>You can remove, view and clear raining content.</p>
